<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #f7f5f0;
      --surface: #ffffff;
      --accent: #c94040;
      --text: #1a1a1a;
      --muted: #6b6b6b;
      --border: #e4e0d8;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    header {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .logo-icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .logo-icon svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; fill: white; }

    .logo-text {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    main {
      padding: 4rem 0 6rem;
    }

    .page-title {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .page-meta {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .section {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--text);
      padding-left: 1rem;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    }

    p {
      color: #3a3a3a;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      color: #3a3a3a;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    ul li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }

    a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    a:hover { border-bottom-color: var(--accent); }

    .highlight-box {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .highlight-box p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 2rem 0;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <div class="logo-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 5.084 3.163 9.426 7.627 11.174-.105-.949-.2-2.405.042-3.441.218-.937 1.407-5.965 1.407-5.965s-.359-.719-.359-1.782c0-1.668.967-2.914 2.171-2.914 1.023 0 1.518.769 1.518 1.69 0 1.029-.655 2.568-.994 3.995-.283 1.194.599 2.169 1.777 2.169 2.133 0 3.772-2.249 3.772-5.495 0-2.873-2.064-4.882-5.012-4.882-3.414 0-5.418 2.561-5.418 5.207 0 1.031.397 2.138.893 2.738a.36.36 0 0 1 .083.345l-.333 1.36c-.053.22-.174.267-.402.161-1.499-.698-2.436-2.889-2.436-4.649 0-3.785 2.75-7.262 7.929-7.262 4.163 0 7.398 2.967 7.398 6.931 0 4.136-2.607 7.464-6.227 7.464-1.216 0-2.359-.632-2.75-1.378l-.748 2.853c-.271 1.043-1.002 2.35-1.492 3.146C9.57 23.812 10.763 24 12 24c6.627 0 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <span class="logo-text">Auto Poster App</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="page-meta">Last updated: <span id="date"></span></p>

    <div class="highlight-box">
      <p>This application is a personal automation tool that posts images to Pinterest via the Pinterest API. We do not collect, store, or share any personal data from users or third parties.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>This application does not collect any personal information. The app operates as a local automation tool and does not have a user-facing interface that gathers data.</p>
      <p>The only data processed by the application includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Image files stored locally on your own device</li>
        <li>Pinterest OAuth2 access tokens, stored locally and used solely to authenticate with the Pinterest API</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
      <p>The application uses your Pinterest OAuth2 credentials exclusively to publish pins to your Pinterest account on your behalf. No data is transmitted to any third party other than Pinterest's own API.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
      <p>All data, including access tokens and image files, is stored locally on your own device. The application does not use any external database or cloud storage.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>This application integrates with the Pinterest API. When using Pinterest's services, you are subject to <a href="https://policy.pinterest.com/en/privacy-policy" target="_blank">Pinterest's Privacy Policy</a>. We do not control and are not responsible for Pinterest's data practices.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer any information to third parties. The application does not share any data with anyone.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>6. Security</h2>
      <p>Since all data is stored locally on your device, the security of your data depends on the security of your own system. We recommend keeping your device secure and not sharing your OAuth credentials with others.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>This application is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at: <a href="mailto:your@email.com">your@email.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <p>&copy; <span id="year"></span> Auto Poster App. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  const now = new Date();
  document.getElementById('date').textContent = now.toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' });
  document.getElementById('year').textContent = now.getFullYear();
</script>

</body>
</html>
